  "dialogue": {
    "title": "他正在等他爱人呢",
    "lines": [
      {
        "speaker": "Narrator",
        "chinese": "这家商店的东西正在大减价,商店里顾客真不少,有的正在挑东西,有的正在排队交钱。",
        "pinyin": "Zhè jiā shāngdiàn de dōngxi zhèngzài dà jiǎnjià, shāngdiàn li gùkè zhēn bu shǎo, yǒude zhèngzài tiāo dōngxi, yǒude zhèngzài pái duì jiāo qián.",
        "english": "This shop is having a big sale. There are quite a lot of customers in the shop. Some are choosing goods, and some are queuing to pay."
      },
      {
        "speaker": "Customer",
        "chinese": "咦,这位先生在做什么呢?他正在等他的爱人呢。",
        "pinyin": "Yī, zhè wèi xiānsheng zài zuò shénme ne? Tā zhèngzài děng tā de aìren ne.",
        "english": "Hey, what is this gentleman doing? He is waiting for his lover."
      },
      {
        "speaker": "Narrator",
        "chinese": "小雨最近很忙,他正在找工作。刚才我去他那儿的时候,他正在给一家公司打电话。听说这家公司正在招聘职员,他打算去应聘。",
        "pinyin": "Xiǎo yǔ zuìjìn hěn máng, tā zhèngzài zhǎo gōngzuò. Gāngcái wǒ qù tā nàr de shíhou, tā zhèngzài gěi yī jiā gōngsī dǎ diànhuà. Tīng shuō zhè jiā gōngsī zhèngzài zhāopìn zhíyuán, tā dǎsuàn qù yìngpìn.",
        "english": "Xiaoyu is very busy recently. He is looking for a job. When I went to his place just now, he was making a phone call to a company. I heard that the company is recruiting staff, and he plans to apply."
      },
      {
        "speaker": "Narrator",
        "chinese": "外边正在下雨,莉莉跟朋友们在房间里一边喝咖啡一边聊天儿。莉莉问大家：明年的这个时候,你们可能在做什么?",
        "pinyin": "Wàibian zhèngzài xià yǔ, Lìli gen péngyoumen zài fángjiān li yībǐan hē kāfei yībǐan liáo tiānr. Lìli wèn dàjiā: Míngniān de zhè ge shíhou, nǐmen kěnéng zài zuò shénme?",
        "english": "It is raining outside. Lili and her friends are in the room, drinking coffee while chatting. Lili asks everyone: What might you be doing this time next year?"
      }
    ]
  },
